# Superbru → Telegram scheduler.
# Runs the tick every minute; the tick itself decides if anything is due and
# only sends each match once (recorded in data/sent.json).
#
# Install with:  crontab deploy/crontab.example
# (edit the path and node location first: `which node`)

* * * * * cd /home/YOU/superbru && /usr/bin/node src/cli/tick.js >> data/tick.log 2>&1
